.fade70
  .container
    .col-md-6
      %h1 When did you last do something with friends?
      %h3.lead You'd love a day or night out, or even a small break away somewhere to catch up but
      %ul#problems
        %li Your friends are unable to pick dates and times
        %li Getting a firm commitment is a nightmare
        %li Theres always someone who drops out
